#. Tag: para
#: systemd.xml:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists information about the status of services. The &systemd; command shows details such as description, executable, status, cgroup, and messages last issued by a service (see <xref linkend=\"sec-boot-systemd-basics-services-debugging\"/> ). The level of details displayed with the System V init differs from service to service."
msgstr ""

