#. Tag: para
#: systemd.xml:1795
#, no-c-format
msgid "&systemd; comes with its own logging mechanism ( <quote>The Journal</quote> ) that logs system messages. This allows you to display the service messages together with status messages. The <command>status</command> command works similar to <command>tail</command> and can also display the log messages in different formats, making it a powerful debugging tool."
